      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1922_AS_RBH_00004"/>Hrn Dr. Rich Beer-Hofmann</addrLine><addrLine>aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40332">Meyerhofen</rs></addrLine><addrLine>im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40471">Zillerthal</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb423">Tirol</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1922_AS_RBH_00003"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb797">Berchtesgaden</rs> mit dem <rs type="place" ref="#pmb52599">Watzmann</rs></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1922_AS_RBH_00004"/>Herzliche <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02391-1"/>Grüße<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02391-1">Der Stempel erlaubt die Einordnung in den <date>August 1922</date>, durch <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzlers</rs> Anreise am <ref target="1922-08-10" type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="date-only"/> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmanns</rs> Abreise aus seiner
                  Urlaubsdestination um den <date>28. 8. 1922</date> ist das Zeitfenster weiter
                  eingeschränkt.</note>!</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>ArthurS</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
